{"tid":868541,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門龍門居連劈7口價賣300萬　重返去年9月水平","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T07:21:17.000Z","uid":28245,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"41b05c78abbf7c30fc20b641ced02a944f8fed6f","tid":868541,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:28:56.000Z","msg":"市況回落，資助房屋出現劈價潮。祥益地產黃慶德表示，屯門居屋龍門居3座中層D室，實用面積484方呎，單位於10月初放盤，於未補地價第二市場叫價400萬港元，其後業主有感市況不佳，累減7口價後，以300萬元售出物業，呎價僅6,198元。 <br />\n<br />\n代理又指，7月同面積單位曾以416萬元成交，是次成交價較高為回落約28%，而是次售價更重返2017年9月的水平。"},{"pid":"e74df7b42c8ed74a048033dac8438d7bd2c749cf","tid":868541,"uid":134834,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:29:54.000Z","msg":"自住驚閪喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5c722488bc6d8df6d52c57ede15f9827a45b42","tid":868541,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74df7b42c8ed74a048033dac8438d7bd2c749cf","tid":868541,"uid":134834,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:29:54.000Z","msg":"自住驚閪喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"咁跌法 點挨"},{"pid":"261fb2625918637c819e9cbd2546e6687c0e67f6","tid":868541,"uid":134834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b5c722488bc6d8df6d52c57ede15f9827a45b42","tid":868541,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74df7b42c8ed74a048033dac8438d7bd2c749cf","tid":868541,"uid":134834,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:29:54.000Z","msg":"自住驚閪喵<img s